{"title":"hu","content":"Rozbudowa tego skryptu o dedykowany panel ustawień to świetny krok, który znacznie zwiększy jego elastyczność. Aby to osiągnąć, stworzyłem pływający (modalny) panel konfiguracyjny z interfejsem graficznym.
Skrypt został zaktualizowany o następujące elementy:
 1. **Zapisywanie stanu w localStorage:** Twoje ustawienia przetrwają odświeżenie strony i ponowne uruchomienie przeglądarki.
 2. **Ustawienia kolorów (Globalne):** Możliwość zmiany koloru tła i tekstu całej strony (nadpisuje domyślne style YMS).
 3. **Pasek na górze (Top Bar):** Zestaw przełączników (checkboxów), które pozwalają ukryć lub pokazać poszczególne wskaźniki (np. NICART, Tractors, Empties).
 4. **Dostrajanie wyszukiwania:** Możliwość zmiany dynamicznie podświetlanej trasy (zamiast wpisanego na sztywno "WRO5->BCN4" możesz wpisać dowolny ciąg, np. "WRO5->MAD4") oraz wyboru koloru tego podświetlenia.
Poniżej znajduje się kompletny, zmodyfikowany kod. Możesz wkleić go bezpośrednio do Tampermonkey:
```javascript
// ==UserScript==
// @name         YMS Design Changes
// @namespace    https://phonetool.amazon.com/users/johjason
// @version      0.3.0.0
// @description  Various design changes to make the YMS Dashboard neater, easier and more functional. With Settings Panel.
// @author       johjason & You
// @downloadURL  https://axzile.corp.amazon.com/-/carthamus/download_script/yms-design-changes.user.js
// @updateURL    https://axzile.corp.amazon.com/-/carthamus/download_script/yms-design-changes.user.js
// @match        https://trans-logistics.amazon.com/yms/shipclerk/*
// @match        https://trans-logistics-eu.amazon.com/yms/shipclerk/*
// @icon         https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/G/01/TransCentral/images/favicon.ico
// @resource     REMOTE_CSS https://drive.corp.amazon.com/view/TOM%20Utilities/TamperMonkey/YMS%20Design%20Changes/newstyle.css?ver=1.5
// @resource     LIGHT_CSS https://drive.corp.amazon.com/view/TOM%20Utilities/TamperMonkey/YMS%20Design%20Changes/newstyle.css?ver=1.5
// @resource     DARK_CSS https://drive.corp.amazon.com/view/TOM%20Utilities/TamperMonkey/YMS%20Design%20Changes/newstyle.dark.css?ver=1.5
// @grant        GM_getResourceText
// @grant        GM_addStyle
// @require      https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.0.min.js
// @run-at       document-end
// ==/UserScript==

/* globals $ */

(function (window, document) {
    window.onload = init;

    GM_addStyle(GM_getResourceText("REMOTE_CSS"));

    // Default configuration for Settings
    const defaultConfig = {
        bgColor: "",
        textColor: "",
        searchRoute: "WRO5->BCN4",
        routeColor: "#ffeb3b",
        metrics: {
            emptyazng: true,
            dockempty: true,
            taggedazng: true,
            loadedAZNG: true,
            ddemptydiv: true,
            tdrout: true,
            psemptydiv: true,
            nonazng: true,
            tractors: true,
            nicarts: true,
            wro5bcn4div: true
        }
    };

    // Load config from localStorage or use defaults
    let ymsConfig = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('ymsSettingsConfig')) || defaultConfig;

    // Dodanie stylów FUI dla przycisku kopiowania i panelu ustawień
    GM_addStyle(`
        .oxy-copy-btn {
            background: transparent;
            color: #f36c00;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            border-radius: 0 !important;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Roboto Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            cursor: pointer;
            user-select: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
            height: 20px;
        }
        .oxy-copy-btn:hover { background: #f36c00; color: #FFFFFF; }
        .oxy-copy-btn:active { opacity: 0.8; }

        #trailerdashboard .empty,
        #trailerdashboard .emptyalert { display: inline-block; min-width: 1.5em; }
        #trailerdashboard .emptyalert { color: #c00; font-weight: bold; }
        .vehicleIdGroup-LP { display: flex; align-items: center; }
        .shipclerk-bold-label { font-size: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; }
        .shipclerk-seals { color: #f36c00 !important; display: flex; justify-content: left; align-items: center; height: 30px !important; width: 10rem; transition: all 0.2s; z-index: 99; font-size: 1rem; background: transparent; padding-left: 0.5rem; }
        .shipclerk-seals:hover { background: #000; transform: scale(3); color: #FFFFFF !important; }
        .vehicle-number-LP { color: rgb(0, 72, 188); transition: all 0.15s; padding: 0.1rem 0.2rem; height: 20px; }
        .vehicle-number-LP:hover { background: var(--bg); color: rgb(50, 188, 0); transform: scale(4) translateX(0px); background: #000; }

        /* Style panelu ustawień */
        #yms-settings-modal {
            display: none; position: fixed; top: 10%; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: #232f3e; color: #fff; padding: 25px; z-index: 10000;
            border: 2px solid #f36c00; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
            width: 450px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-height: 80vh; overflow-y: auto;
        }
        #yms-settings-modal h2 { color: #f36c00; margin-top: 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #555; padding-bottom: 10px; }
        #yms-settings-modal h3 { font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: #ff9900; }
        #yms-settings-modal .setting-group { margin-bottom: 15px; background: #131921; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; }
        #yms-settings-modal label { display: block; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 5px; cursor: pointer; }
        #yms-settings-modal input[type="text"] { width: 100%; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box; background: #fff; color: #000; border: 1px solid #ccc; }
        .yms-btn { background: #f36c00; color: #fff; border: none; padding: 8px 15px; cursor: pointer; border-radius: 3px; font-weight: bold; width: 100%; margin-top:10px; }
        .yms-btn:hover { background: #d35400; }
        #open-yms-settings { margin-left: 20px; background: #232f3e; border: 1px solid #f36c00; color: #f36c00; padding: 2px 10px; cursor: pointer; border-radius: 3px; font-weight: bold; }
        #open-yms-settings:hover { background: #f36c00; color: #fff; }
    `);

    // Iniekcja dynamicznych kolorów strony z poziomu ustawień
    function applyCustomColors() {
        let customStyle = document.getElementById("yms-custom-colors-style");
        if (!customStyle) {
            customStyle = document.createElement("style");
            customStyle.id = "yms-custom-colors-style";
            document.head.appendChild(customStyle);
        }

        let cssRules = "";
        if (ymsConfig.bgColor) cssRules += `body, .app-body, .flex-container { background-color: ${ymsConfig.bgColor} !important; } `;
        if (ymsConfig.textColor) cssRules += `body, span, div, td, th { color: ${ymsConfig.textColor} !important; } `;

        customStyle.innerHTML = cssRules;
    }

    // Aplikuj kolory od razu przy starcie
    applyCustomColors();

    function init() {
        "use strict";

        // 1. Zbudowanie Kontenerów Opcji i Przycisku Ustawień
        document.getElementById("mainContainer").insertAdjacentHTML(
            "beforebegin",
            `
            <div id="custom-options-container" style="display:flex; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
                <h3 id="dark-mode-label" style="margin-right:10px;"><t>Dark Mode:</t></h3>
                <div id="dark-mode-switch" style="margin-right:20px;">
                    <input id="dark-mode-toggle" type="checkbox">
                    <label for="dark-mode-toggle"></label>
                </div>
                <h3 id="filterTrailer-label" style="margin-right:10px;"><t>Tagged Trailers:</t></h3>
                <div>
                    <input id="filterTrailer-toggle" type="checkbox">
                    <label for="filterTrailer"></label>
                </div>
                <button id="open-yms-settings">⚙️ Settings</button>
            </div>
            `
        );

        // 2. Wbudowanie Panelu Konfiguracyjnego (Modal)
        document.body.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', `
            <div id="yms-settings-modal">
                <h2>Ustawienia YMS Dashboard</h2>

                <div class="setting-group">
                    <h3>1. Kolory strony (Zostaw puste dla domyślnych)</h3>
                    <label>Kolor tła: <input type="color" id="cfg-bg-color" value="${ymsConfig.bgColor || '#ffffff'}"></label>
                    <label>Kolor tekstu: <input type="color" id="cfg-text-color" value="${ymsConfig.textColor || '#000000'}"></label>
                </div>

                <div class="setting-group" id="cfg-metrics-group">
                    <h3>2. Elementy na górnym pasku</h3>
                    <label><input type="checkbox" data-id="emptyazng"> AZNG Empties in PS</label>
                    <label><input type="checkbox" data-id="dockempty"> AZNG Empties on DD</label>
                    <label><input type="checkbox" data-id="taggedazng"> Tagged AZNG Trailers</label>
                    <label><input type="checkbox" data-id="loadedAZNG"> Loaded AZNG w/ No VRID</label>
                    <label><input type="checkbox" data-id="ddemptydiv"> Open Dock Doors</label>
                    <label><input type="checkbox" data-id="tdrout"> Doors TDR'd Out</label>
                    <label><input type="checkbox" data-id="psemptydiv"> Open Slips</label>
                    <label><input type="checkbox" data-id="nonazng"> OnSite Non AZNG Emptys</label>
                    <label><input type="checkbox" data-id="tractors"> Tractors</label>
                    <label><input type="checkbox" data-id="nicarts"> NICART Loads</label>
                    <label><input type="checkbox" data-id="wro5bcn4div"> Dynamiczny Alert Trasy (np. WRO5->BCN4)</label>
                </div>

                <div class="setting-group">
                    <h3>3. Dostrajanie wyszukiwania danych</h3>
                    <label>Obserwowana trasa (domyślnie WRO5->BCN4):</label>
                    <input type="text" id="cfg-search-route" value="${ymsConfig.searchRoute}">
                    <br><br>
                    <label>Kolor podświetlenia trasy: <input type="color" id="cfg-route-color" value="${ymsConfig.routeColor}"></label>
                </div>

                <button id="save-yms-settings" class="yms-btn">Zapisz i Odśwież widok</button>
                <button id="close-yms-settings" style="background:transparent; color:#ccc; border:1px solid #ccc; padding:8px 15px; cursor:pointer; width:100%; margin-top:5px;">Anuluj</button>
            </div>
        `);

        // Obsługa modala ustawień
        $("#open-yms-settings").click(function() {
            // Populate checkboxes based on config
            $("#cfg-metrics-group input[type='checkbox']").each(function() {
                let id = $(this).data("id");
                $(this).prop("checked", ymsConfig.metrics[id] !== false); // default to true if undefined
            });
            $("#yms-settings-modal").fadeIn();
        });

        $("#close-yms-settings").click(function() {
            $("#yms-settings-modal").fadeOut();
        });

        $("#save-yms-settings").click(function() {
            ymsConfig.bgColor = $("#cfg-bg-color").val() !== "#ffffff" && $("#cfg-bg-color").val() !== "#000000" ? $("#cfg-bg-color").val() : "";
            ymsConfig.textColor = $("#cfg-text-color").val() !== "#ffffff" && $("#cfg-text-color").val() !== "#000000" ? $("#cfg-text-color").val() : "";
            ymsConfig.searchRoute = $("#cfg-search-route").val() || "WRO5->BCN4";
            ymsConfig.routeColor = $("#cfg-route-color").val();

            $("#cfg-metrics-group input[type='checkbox']").each(function() {
                let id = $(this).data("id");
                ymsConfig.metrics[id] = $(this).is(":checked");
            });

            localStorage.setItem('ymsSettingsConfig', JSON.stringify(ymsConfig));
            applyCustomColors();
            updateTopBarVisibility();
            $("#yms-settings-modal").fadeOut();
            emptyAZNG(); // Wymuś odświeżenie paska
        });

        // ----------------------------------------------------------------------
        // Funkcje Dark Mode i Filter
        document.getElementById("dark-mode-toggle").addEventListener("change", function () {
            if (document.getElementById("dark-mode-toggle").checked) {
                GM_addStyle(GM_getResourceText("DARK_CSS"));
            } else {
                GM_addStyle(GM_getResourceText("LIGHT_CSS"));
            }
        });

        document.getElementById("filterTrailer-toggle").addEventListener("change", function () {
            if (document.getElementById("filterTrailer-toggle").checked) {
                $("#ship-clerk-dashboard-table tbody tr").show();
                var targChecked = $(".flex-container.row").filter(function () {
                    return $(this).children(".yard-asset-yellow,.yard-asset-red").length == 0;
                });
                var targCheckedEmpty = $(".masterYardLP td:nth-child(2):not('[class^=col2]')");
                var targCheckedCombined = targChecked.add(targCheckedEmpty);
                $(targCheckedCombined).closest("tr").not("tr tr").hide();
            } else {
                $("#ship-clerk-dashboard-table tbody tr").show();
                var targUnchecked = $(".flex-container.row").filter(function () {
                    return $(this).children(".yard-asset-yellow,.yard-asset-red").length == 0;
                });
                var targUncheckedEmpty = $(".masterYardLP td:nth-child(2):not('[class^=col2]')");
                var targUncheckedCombined = targUnchecked.add(targUncheckedEmpty);
                $(targUncheckedCombined).closest("tr").not("tr tr").show();
            }
        });

        function updateTopBarVisibility() {
            // Ukrywamy / pokazujemy nagłówki H2 w zależności od konfiguracji
            for (let metricId in ymsConfig.metrics) {
                let elem = document.getElementById(metricId);
                if (elem && elem.parentElement) {
                    elem.parentElement.style.display = ymsConfig.metrics[metricId] ? "" : "none";
                }
            }
        }

        if (window.location.href.indexOf("shipclerk/#/yard") > -1) {
            document.styleSheets[0].insertRule(".note-present-icon {flex-shrink: 0;}");
            document.getElementById("mainContainer").insertAdjacentHTML(
                "beforebegin",
                `
